Title: The Dark... Whatever
Plot: Dexter is unnerved when Hannah's father pays him a surprise visit; the Phantom Arsonist's crimes become more vicious; and Quinn defends Nadia's honor and finds himself in a volatile situation. Meanwhile; LaGuerta asks a former superior for help on the Bay Harbor Butcher case.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence,offensive language and sexual themes
Writer: Lauren Gussis, Jace Richdale, Scott Reynolds
